{
  "word":"πέπων",
  "short":"'softie'",
  "medium":"familiar, 'softie'",
  "long":"familiar form of address, literally something like 'softie'",
  "notes":"Used in the vocative, πέπον, πέπονες. Literally ripe, connoting softness, perhaps like 'you old softie.' Usually positive but sometimes used to reproach someone for softness. "
